content: I tried to register my phone number and it did not work. I tried multiple times and had my son try to help me. it says its already registered  to a discord account. I reset my password and logged back in to  my account. It still did not work. So what do I do now? PLEASE HELP!!
Hello <@1269431206697766915> I can help you with this. Would you like me to write it all here, or would you prefer to screenshare on Zoom?

The steps are explained on this Discord page with screenshots.
**Important: use a DIFFERENT email on the second account when you remove the phone.** 
https://support.discord.com/hc/en-us/articles/4413460214807-How-to-Remove-a-Phone-Number#h_01FQFTDJQP5D3XMMSDT3CJQGPR
i dont have a second account. This is the only discord i have

It is common to have a second "accidental" account. The instructions will help you reach that account and release the phone number. This does work, I have guided many folks through it already.
However, I respect your judgement and if you believe you only have one account, then you can contact Discord support and wait for them to get back to you. https://dis.gd/contact
